Narrowing the skills gap, one video at a time.

Boston PHP is All In with AI. LinkedIn Learning has made Getting Started with Prompt Engineering available for FREE for a limited time. This Learning Path contains six courses and more than six hours of training material. Upon completing each course you will receive a certificate you can post to your LinkedIn profile. In addition, you will receive a Learning Path certificate once you complete all six courses. All you need to begin is a LinkedIn account.

This Learning Path includes the following courses:

Introduction to Prompt Engineering for Generative AI
Top 10 AI Prompts
Prompt Engineering with Gemini
Introduction to Multimodal Prompting for Generative AI
Prompt Engineering and AI Agents with ChatGPT
AI Agents Made Simple: Your Zero-to-Hero Guide to Prompting for Work Automation
